OL,3,CGuernsey could face water shortage
OL,4,Cafter pesticide pollutes reservoir
OL,6,FGuernsey has banned a pesticide after
OL,7,Fit was found in the island's largest
OL,8,Freservoir.
OL,10,FMetamitron, which is used as a
OL,11,Fweedkiller, was discovered in a
OL,12,Froutine water quality sample at Longue
OL,13,FHougue Reservoir in February, with
OL,14,Fsupply from the area cut off for
OL,15,Fpublic safety while further
OL,16,Finvestigations were carried out.
OL,18,FThe reservoir holds 27% of the
OL,19,Fisland's water supply.
