OL,3,CGuernsey could face water shortage
OL,4,Cafter pesticide pollutes reservoir
OL,6,FAlthough it is not known exactly where
OL,7,Fthe chemical came from, it is believed
OL,8,Fto have drained into the reservoir in
OL,9,FJanuary from a water source which
OL,10,Fflows from the centre of the island.
OL,12,FGuernsey Water says that while there
OL,13,Fis no threat to islanders' health as
OL,14,Fthe polluted water has been contained,
OL,15,Fthey are concerned about the wider
OL,16,Fsupply given that water from Longue
OL,17,FHougue is now only being used in
OL,18,Freduced volumes.
OL,20,FAny shortage could be compounded by
OL,21,Fthe current dry weather.
