OL,3,CGuernsey could face water shortage
OL,4,Cafter pesticide pollutes reservoir
OL,6,FDaffyd Griffiths, Guernsey Water's
OL,7,FQuality Risk Manager, said: "Although
OL,8,Fthis situation is far from ideal, with
OL,9,Fthe island's largest water resource
OL,10,Fnow only able to provide a very
OL,11,Flimited supply of water, thanks to our
OL,12,Frigorous testing schedules, metamitron
OL,13,Fwas detected early enough to protect
OL,14,Fthe island's drinking water.
