OL,3,CGuernsey could face water shortage
OL,4,Cafter pesticide pollutes reservoir
OL,6,FThey hope this will help reduce any
OL,7,Frun-off into water courses.
OL,9,FSome water from Longue Hougue is being
OL,10,Fused in Guernsey's supply and diluted
OL,11,Fwith water from other reservoirs.
OL,13,FGuernsey Water says recent testing on
OL,14,Fdrinking water proves that metamitron
OL,15,Fhas been completely removed.
OL,17,FMr Griffiths added that if water is
OL,18,Fcontaminated again and the current dry
OL,19,Fweather continues, restrictions on
OL,20,Fwater usage could come into force.
